Paper: hep-th/9508137

Date: 1995-08-25

Title: Quantum oscillator and a bound system of two dyons

Authors: V. M. Ter--Antonyan, A. Nersessian

Comments: 6 pages, LaTeX, corrections in Introduction

Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A10 (1995) 2633-2638

It is shown that $U(1)$--Hamiltonian reduction of a four--dimensionalisotropic quantum oscillator results in a bound system of two spinlessSchwinger's dyons. Its wavefunctions and spectrum are constructed.